{"tid":1749092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果日報推薦名單  11.24光復區議會","createTime":"2019-11-24T01:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T02:08:51.000Z","uid":340042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"491b40bb88de85c8b366fdd06496350c37349653","tid":1749092,"uid":340042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:57:20.000Z","msg":"今次區選，是反送中運動後首場全港大型選舉，民主派動員參與，但逾千名候選人中，潛藏不少偽黃絲、假獨立、隱形左派，甚至鎅票黨，企圖混淆視聽。《蘋果》區選網站，詳列各區候選人名單，讓選民認清手中一票，投向良知一方，不但要踢走保皇黨，更是向當權者明確表態，五大訴求，缺一不可，警暴惡行，更要追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n從街頭到議會，兩條戰線，一同抗暴。由加油、反抗、報仇，到了今天，香港人，投票！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60298586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60298586&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=5f4618e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60298586&h=af71fbeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60298586</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bazdes7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBazdes7.jpg&h=79946230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzDmomt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqzDmomt.jpg&h=af8a0d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtCyes8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtCyes8.jpg&h=b3ea54fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NY1WceP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNY1WceP.jpg&h=f68811a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCfLP1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCfLP1v.jpg&h=b577afec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77SN3mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=